      "term": "biocontrols",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "B2",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun (plural)",
          "definition": "The methods or agents that biologically control pests, such as predators, parasites, or diseases used to reduce pest populations.",
          "examples": [
            "Farmers adopted biocontrols to manage aphids without chemicals.",
            "Biocontrols are a key part of integrated pest management."
